# ============================================================================
# Approval Policy
# ============================================================================
#
# Routes and components listed above require explicit approval from code owners
# before merge when changes affect:
#
# 1. Visual appearance (Chromatic diff approval required)
# 2. Role-based access control (RBAC policy review required)
# 3. Telemetry or data emission (security review required)
# 4. Accessibility compliance (a11y validation required)
#
# Default: 1 approval required (code owner)
# Override: Can be relaxed for maintenance-only changes via automation
